## ðŸ“¥ Installation

### ðŸ”¹ From PyPI

```bash
pip install py-json-analyzer
```

Upgrade to the latest version:

```bash
pip install --upgrade py-json-analyzer
```

### ðŸ”¹ From Source

```bash
git clone https://github.com/MS-32154/py-json-analyzer
cd json_explorer
pip install .
```

### ðŸ”¹ Development Mode

```bash
pip install -e .
```

